  3.9572785281875896`*^9}},ExpressionUUID->"eb6fa357-27b2-814c-bd4b-\
1bb24fef4467"],

Cell["\<\
Specify the particles in the multiplets and the factors in the Hamiltonian. \
Elements must be ordered from highest to lowest m within multiplets. Particle \
multiplets must be a list of strings corresponding to the names of the \
particles, and the Hamiltonian list may contain symbolic variables and \
expressions.\
\>", "Text",
 CellChangeTimes->{{3.9669591818431606`*^9, 3.96695918508737*^9}, {
  3.966959215130106*^9, 3.966959249026575*^9}, {3.970784561795349*^9, 
  3.9707846474347897`*^9}, {3.978614081796379*^9, 3.9786140842044945`*^9}, {
