\(s\), \(0\)]\) \[Rule] \!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(D\), \(0\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(\[CapitalDelta]\), \(-\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[SuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(\[CapitalSigma]\), \
\(_\)], \(*\)], \(+\)]\))", 
      3 "\[CapitalGamma](\!\(\*SubsuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(B\), \(_\)], \
\(d\), \(0\)]\) \[Rule] \!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(D\), \(0\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[SuperscriptBox[\(\[CapitalXi]\), \(*\)], \(-\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[SuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(\[CapitalXi]\), \(_\)], \
\(*\)], \(+\)]\))" - 3 
      "\[CapitalGamma](\!\(\*SubsuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(B\), \(_\)], \
\(d\), \(0\)]\) \[Rule] \!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(D\), \(0\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[SuperscriptBox[\(\[CapitalSigma]\), \(*\)], \(-\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[SuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(\[CapitalSigma]\), \
\(_\)], \(*\)], \(+\)]\))" + 
      "\[CapitalGamma](\!\(\*SubsuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(B\), \(_\)], \
\(d\), \(0\)]\) \[Rule] \!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(D\), \(0\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(\[CapitalDelta]\), \(-\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(\[CapitalDelta]\), \(_\)], \(+\)]\))" - 
      "\[CapitalGamma](\!\(\*SubsuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(B\), \(_\)], \
\(d\), \(0\)]\) \[Rule] \!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(D\), \(0\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(\[CapitalOmega]\), \(-\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(\[CapitalOmega]\), \(_\)], \(+\)]\))" - 
      3 "\[CapitalGamma](\!\(\*SubsuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(B\), \(_\)], \
\(s\), \(0\)]\) \[Rule] \!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(D\), \(0\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[SuperscriptBox[\(\[CapitalXi]\), \(*\)], \(-\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[SuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(\[CapitalXi]\), \(_\)], \
\(*\)], \(+\)]\))" + 
      3 "\[CapitalGamma](\!\(\*SubsuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(B\), \(_\)], \
\(s\), \(0\)]\) \[Rule] \!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(D\), \(0\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[SuperscriptBox[\(\[CapitalSigma]\), \(*\)], \(-\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[SuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(\[CapitalSigma]\), \
\(_\)], \(*\)], \(+\)]\))" - 
      "\[CapitalGamma](\!\(\*SubsuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(B\), \(_\)], \
\(s\), \(0\)]\) \[Rule] \!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(D\), \(0\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(\[CapitalDelta]\), \(-\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(\[CapitalDelta]\), \(_\)], \(+\)]\))" + 
      "\[CapitalGamma](\!\(\*SubsuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(B\), \(_\)], \
\(s\), \(0\)]\) \[Rule] \!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(D\), \(0\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[\(\[CapitalOmega]\), \(-\)]\) \
\!\(\*SuperscriptBox[OverscriptBox[\(\[CapitalOmega]\), \(_\)], \(+\)]\))"}]]],
  Editable->False]], "Print",
